1)(2)(3)(4)中可以推出  \u003cb\u003e宇宙是圆的\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560771130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e6c58a8ffed3fc3571fca06069d35a26","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560771130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545886396,"updated_time":1545886462,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e看了这么多的回答，总结一下。有冷嘲热讽的，有劝题主好好学习上个好大学的，有吃瓜群众的，有坐等见证历史的。但是最重要的一点是，有没有新的数学概念或理论诞生。以题主的知识来看，如果你是用初等数学解决了这个问题，对数学的推动或贡献可能微不足道。毕竟数学猜想的难题的价值不在于有多难，而是在解决的过程中能启发人们产生新的数学概念或理论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e举个例子，许多数学家如高斯欧拉都没能证明费马大定理，于是有人劝希尔伯特去解决这个难题，他却说不想杀死这只下金蛋的鹅。为什么他这么说？因为在对费马大定理长达三个世纪的求证过程中，诞生了许多数学概念和理论，还开拓了新的数学分支。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e瞧，问题不在证明之后会不会带来保送，职位，经济等无关数学的东西。而是证明本身带来了什么，能够促进我们对数学的理解？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=440\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=400\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
